  "type": "equipment",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This union of chains, metal plates, and magically solidified blood has a brutally functional appearance. Designed in cooperation with the pain-loving kytons of the Shadow Plane, kyton bloodsuits include clusters of blades and needles on the inside of the armor that shift about, seeking to pierce the wearer&rsquo;s skin. The armor deals 1d4 damage to you each minute of operation (whenever the armor uses a charge). When you take this damage, you can spend 1 Resolve Point as a reaction to restore 5 charges to the kyton bloodsuit, but you can&rsquo;t restore more charges than it actually holds.</p>",
